<br>
Stealth - reduce the refresh timer on Hide and Sneak skills.  Effectively gives us better aggro management (at least with the Hide skill). Use the same costs/progression as Fast Feign for monks.  Class ability (rogue).<br>
<br>
Improved Assassinate - allow higher level mobs to be assassinated.  Even a +1 level per skill ability would be nice.  Class ability (rogue).<br>
<br>
Assassinate &lt;creature type&gt; - Allow rogues to assassinate creatures other than humaniods and oozes.  Could have a seperate skill for each creature type, or have some tiered progression that includes all creture types.  Class ability (rogue)<br>
<br>
Improved Haste - +2%/+5%/+10% haste for melee attacks, stacks with all other haste effects.  Raises haste cap by same amount.  Archetype ability (melee, hybrids)<br>
<br>
Offhand Training - Provides damage bonus for offhand weapon.  Archetype ability (melee, hybrids).<br>
<br>
Shadowstep - In play flavor: Rogue steps into the shadows and appears somewhere else in the zone.  Basically would take you to the safe spot of the zone (think succor).  Class ability (rogue).<br>
<br>
Improved Attack - Raises ATK.  Could use the same costs as stat increases (just make it useful by providing more than +2 ATK per AA point spent).  General ability (all).  Or have a class ability that raises ATK only when piercing weapons are equiped (rogue, obviously).<br>
<br>
Chaid Duskwalker<br>
TK Assassin of Drinal<br>
<br>
